  <brief_title>A Randomized, Open Label, Clinical Trial of the Pharmacokinetics of Azithromycin Following a Single Dose of Azithromycin Sustained Release (2 Gram) or Commercial Azithromycin Tablet (500 mg) to Cancer Patients That Require Lung Surgery</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Open Label, Clinical Trial of the Pharmacokinetics of Azithromycin in Serum, Bronchial Washings and Lung Tissue Following a Single Dose of Azithromycin Sustained Release (2 Gram) or Commercial Azithromycin Tablet (500 mg) to Cancer Patients That Require Lung Resection</official_title>
  <sponsors>
